				<td colspan="2"><span>I have been playing around with Swarm Kiting in DL.  The concept is pretty straight forward and I have had reasoable success.  
<br />

<br />
My question is:  What is the best way to break charm when you pet is low on health so you can finish him off with a couple chants?
<br />

<br />
Hide does not seem to break charm more than occasionally so I have resorted to using SSC with flute in equipped then when charm breaks I switch out for drum to chant.
<br />

<br />
Any suggestions on better ways to break charm?</span></td>
