			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The Tiny Cloak of Darkest night is good because it fits in Range slot doesn't need to be targeted, as it only affects user.
<br />
On the other hand, it doesn't work until you are lvl 55+.
<br />

<br />
Goblin Gazughi ring is great due to being an insta-cast item with no level restriction and easy to get.
<br />
On the other hand, you must target yourself to use it, and you better have your 'toggle last 2 targets' key set up.
<br />

<br />
I prefer the ring, personally, lets me get the pet down to under 10% easily.  With anything else, you have to really time it carefully or pet dies and you get no xp, or pet charm breaks and you have 15 to 20% life to wack down.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
